snippet.title: Celebrities React To Johnny Depp Winning In Court & Being Rehired... | VS Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Celebrities React To Johnny Depp Winning In Court & Being Rehired... | VS Amber Heard
Johnny Depp has been in an interesting place as of late. He's getting to make movies again (though in a very independent way), and while his court case is still raging on, the momentum does feel like its shifting in his favor. And with that comes an opportunity for him to honestly be happy about where things are going. What's more, he's not the only one to realize this, and thus he's getting a lot of support from people who want to see him exonerated. But what exactly are they saying? We'll break it down for you.
